https://substack.com/redirect/ecde91c2-62be-4f4d-a3ca-55e44096e2b2?j=3DeyJ1=
IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Atomic AI</a><span>), de=
veloped a triple-drug combination, Trifakta, to fight cystic fibrosis. The =
disease impacts 100,000 people worldwide. A study published February this y=
ear showed that </span><strong>Trifakta can increase life expectancy from ~=
30 to over 80 years</strong><span>, or an average of 45.4 years. </span></p=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Ellen Sidransky</strong><span>, </span><strong>A=
